value.raw:
<style>
  :host {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: baseline;
  }
  ::slotted(.heading) {
    mixin(--css-column)
    height: 128px;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }
  ::slotted(.list-item) {
    mixin(--css-row)
    mixin(--css-center)
    width: 100%;
    padding: 12px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
    height: 48px;
  }
  ::slotted(* .flex) {
    mixin(--css-flex)
  }

</style>
<custom-container>
<slot></slot>
</custom-container>
